&lt;li&gt;Act as a key stakeholder and developer customer proxy to Coast&#39;s product engineering teams to build and refine a best-in-class API to Coast&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Successful onboarding of enterprise customers with custom integrations to Coast API (both guided and self-service by customer)&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Drive enterprise acquisition and expansion by leading technical discovery, scoping, and implementation planning to ensure successful integration of Coast into complex customer environments.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
